profile:
The Home Improvement People have completed literally thousands of renovations since our inception. We are a unique award winning contracting company, consulted by various media as industry experts. 
Please view our website at homeimprovementpeople.com to view images of some of our projects. 
For our clients' convenience, we've implemented progress billing as well as financing.
Regardless of scope, we approach every single home renovation with a foundation of strong design aesthetics, comprehensive product options, sound project management, and a commitment to craftsmanship.
 
Our projects range from remodelled bathrooms and kitchens, to rear additions,  hardwood flooring, basements, second story additions and other extensive renovations. We undertake work in all budget ranges.
 
Choosing a reputable contractor is the most important decision you will make regarding your renovation. From plans and permits, to last little finishing details, The Home Improvement People is committed to completing your renovations and home improvements in a professional manner and to your complete satisfaction.
We take pride in our personalized service and our high quality workmanship. 
Call us for quality, insured work - completed on time, and on budget.
416-782-7605.

profile:
We are Design+Build company having all the professionals from A-Z  in our team. 
Before you do anything, give us a call as we are Design + Build company with Tarion new home builder, Structure engineer with 'PNG' license and working with some of the best Interior design and Architectural firms in Toronto. You will be saving so much money by choosing us instead of waisting your money by hiring a individual companies for each task. 

Based in Toronto, 'Fresh Home Innovations' has been a leader in residential renovations and custom home construction since 2000. From concept to completion, we take a client’s vision and make it a reality through a comprehensive process to ensure the finished product exceeds expectations. Choosing a reputable contractor is the most important decision you will make regarding your project. From plans and permits, to last little finishing details, freshhomeinnovations.com  is committed to completing your renovations and home improvements in a professional manner and to your complete satisfaction.

Our wealth of experience, skilled expertise and attention to detail enables us to offer you innovative solutions, competitive pricing and the ability to meet milestones. We appreciate how much your project means to you. That’s why we approach each project with professionalism, integrity and adaptability while maintaining open communication with you every step of the way. 
We pride ourselves in Home additions, renovations, custom home building, commercial renovations, condominium renovations and design and build projects.  Let us partner with you to create the home of your dreams.

We understand the family home is the most important investment most people will make in their lifetime, and you as our client have entrusted your investment to us. So whether it be a new architecturally designed or inspired home, or a renovation and extension of your existing home, you can be guaranteed that Fresh Home Innovations  is most definitely the qualified team for your project.
Our friendly, jovial and courteous staff receive ongoing training to ensure we can deliver this promise to you on a daily basis. 

 We have had the opportunity to transform your dreams into reality by designing rooms where you can relax and your children can safely play. We have enjoyed being a part of homeowners’ lives and strive to continue to provide our customers with the best technology on the market. We have completed literally thousands of renovations since our inception. We are a unique award winning contracting company, consulted by various media as industry experts. 
Please view our website at freshhomeinnovations.com to view images of some of our projects.  
Regardless of scope, we approach every single home renovation with a foundation of strong design aesthetics, comprehensive product options, sound project management, and a commitment to craftsmanship. 

Our projects range from building new custom homes, home additions and extensions, condominium renovations, architectural design and permit, structural engineering, commercial renovations, rear addition, second floor addition, basement underpinning, historical restoration, custom projects, general contracting, custom kitchen and bathrooms, residential renovations and finally we design and build everything. We take pride in our personalized service and our high quality workmanship. 

With a minimum 2 year Warranty, we at freshhomeinnovations.com  know how to design and build lasting results and lasting relationships with each of our highly respected clients. 
Our focus is on Custom projects such as custom Kitchen renovations, Basement Finishing and underpinning, Bathroom Renovation and Bathroom Remodeling, Home Additions, Second Story Additions, Rear Additions, Home Extensions and Rear Extensions, commercial renovations, office renovation, architectural drawings, permit and etc. We work with some of the top architects, interior designers, engineers and sub-trades in Toronto. We provide custom marble and tile install services as our marble and tile setters are highly skilled and detail oriented. We are the all inclusive General Contractor who will take care of all your design and general contracting needs.

Fresh Home Innovations is an innovative, full service design/build/ construction firm based in Toronto, specializing in residential clients across the GTA. With decades of construction management experience on a wide variety of residential projects, we offer a strong design aesthetic, invaluable insight, vast resources and craftsman that exceed client expectations.
Strong leadership and communication skills are the essential components necessary to navigate a construction project from concept to completion. Our extensive knowledge of all trade areas involved in both new construction and sophisticated renovations have proven invaluable to our company and our clients. Our recognition of the importance of scheduling, cost control, and quality control underlies and defines our successful completion of many challenging projects on time and within budget.

There’s many different reasons to work with us: to make room for a growing family, to improve layout or increase the resale value of your property! Our team of professionals offer customers design and build counselling along with skilled trades and top discounts, on top brands. 

There is no substitute for experience. Join the list of satisfied clients! In the end the quality of your project depends on who you hire. When you hire us, you do so because of our company’s reputation, our track record with past clients and our commitment to new ones. The registered DesignBar trademark provides DIY home owners a single source for their residential design and construction needs when buying or selling homes in the GTA.

Future Perfect Construction is a local skilled construction firm founded in 2000 by a select group of individuals with a high level of expertise in the trade. The firm specializes in Commercial and Residential Renovations, Home Inspections, New Home Builds and Construction Project Management. Future Perfect's primary goal of meeting customer's needs through quality workmanship has resulted in the pride, loyalty and trust that co-insides with our standard of excellence. The firm is always working with it's clients to exceed standards, adhere to budgets and manage strict timelines. 
We believe that the value of the dollar has come a long way so we provide our services and do business with the utmost professionalism. We aim to service customers from the initial phase of planning and cost estimates to the final stages of our warranty process. 
Contact us for a free "No Pressure" estimate and let us help you take the first step to completing your project. Advice is always free.

AGM Renovations offers Complete basement and Bathroom renovations packages from the professional design through the professional cleaning including:

Drywall- We employ only professional drywall installers and our goal is deliver complete satisfaction to each and every client with the quality of our workmanship and our prompt, reliable service.
    
Taping- Our drywall taping techniques will bring a high quality smooth finish, with a level of excellence you will take pride in.

Home Additions Builders Basement Renovation Kitchen Planning & Renovation General Contractors 

At Oborne Contracting we pride ourselves on customer service. We specialize in additions, kitchens, bathrooms, basements, and all other home renovation and remodeling needs. Our team is courteous, skilled, conscientious and determined to ensure each project is completed on time and on budget. Our longstanding trades are reliable professionals who are committed to their work and quality. We are confident that you will find at Oborne Contracting we conduct ourselves on a highly professional level, assuring your complete satisfaction is our key to success.Oborne Contracting Inc. has been servicing Toronto and surrounding area home owners for over 20 years. We specialize in custom home building, general contracting, home repairs, design and build, home remodeling and restoration, home additions and basement renovations. 
We take pride in attending to every detail of any project we take on, from the initial meeting with the discerning home owner until after the job is completed. After working with our professional staff you will understand why Oborne Contracting Inc. will be your first choice for all of your home upgrades, renovations and new constructions.

Each home remodeling project is unique in the level of complexity and requirements. This demands a level of experience to design a broad plan and turn any project into a functional and livable home upgrade, addition or custom design. We build our client’s trust by understanding their needs, budgets, time frames, while supervising every step of the construction process. No question is ever left unanswered.

profile:
Valentini Kitchens has been building and renovating Quality Kitchens and Cabinetry since 1974 to the Toronto and surrounding GTA markets. 
Valentini Kitchens is a true "Family Business" that has been owned and operated by the Pasquariello Family for over 45 years. 
Valentini was founded in 1974 by the late Mike Pasquariello and is now run by his 3 sons, Tony, Piero and Marco. 
We at Valentini Kitchens have maintained a high quality standard and reputation from our first day in business, with our attention to detail and service to our customer as our # 1 motive.
 
Today, we have made changes to our business to compete with our changing markets and with our changes we will maintain our quality and service to make sure our clients are 100% satisfied. We have also implemented a few more cost effective lines of Cabinetry, many that are locally sourced and a few off shore lines to meet the changing markets and cost budgets of our clientele.
 
Valentini Kitchens offers Cabinetry in many options to fit your needs and budget:
- Full custom made line of Kitchen, Bath and various types of Cabinetry and Mill Work.
- Semi custom made locally sourced and branded line of Kitchen, Bath, Laundry & Closet Cabinetry.
- Semi custom made off shore sourced and branded line of Kitchen and Bath Cabinetry.

  
Full line of custom made Residential Cabinetry Options including: 
- Kitchens and Bath Cabinetry
- TV, Entertainment and Wall Unit Cabinetry
- Bar and Built In Cabinetry
- Laundry & Mud Room Cabinetry
- Home Office Cabinetry
- Closet Organizers and Home Storage Solutions



Full line of custom made Commercial / Industrial Cabinetry Options including:
- Office Kitchen & Bath Cabinetry 
- Custom Cabinetry for Restaurants, Bars, Coffee Houses, Hair Salon / Spas, Dental and Doctor Offices, etc.

 
When you purchase a service from Valentini, you are buying into a family that has a reputation of giving our customers 100% of Quality, Service and most importantly Price.
Being one of a handful of the GTA'S Cabinetry Pioneers, Valentini is small in size but is evolving with the everyday changes in the world of Woodworking and Full Home Renovations.
Valentini offers a true complete "1 Stop" shopping experience by providing customers with full Renovation capabilities. We can start with an in home or in showroom consultation and the rest is up to the customer. Valentini can take care of full project management from start to completion. We offer a full range of Renovations to complete selection of Retail Products.
What makes us at Valentini Kitchens Unique is that we are one of the only companies that allows consumers to purchase everything directly from us for use on their Home Renovations, meaning "We Install Everything We Sell". By supplying the retail products we sell, we can insure you as the home owner full warranties of the products we use on the job and also "Less Time" having to run around to have all the products ready on the job site. We take care of showing you the products in our own Kitchens and Bath Showroom and the delivery of everything to your home when it is needed for the Renovation.

 
Valentini also offers a full list of Retail Showroom Products including: 
- Premade Bath Vanity Cabinetry
- Tile, Stone and Mosaics
- Hardwood, Vinyl, Laminate and Carpet Flooring
- Quartz, Granite, Marble and Laminate Counter Tops
- Plumbing Fixtures
 



As many companies grow in size, we at Valentini Kitchens want to remain small in size with our 1 Factory Showroom Location, we pride ourselves in maintaining our high standards of Quality, Service and Reputation that has made is one of the leaders in the Kitchen and Renovation Industry for over 4 decades. As a family business, we offer the ultimate hands on approach with any project we take on.

Valentini offers a 1 hour "In home" or "In Showroom" free Estimate Consultation (By Appointment only).
Please Call or Email us with your inquiries today. (Please leave a voice mail message or email us if we are not able to respond the same day as we may be on the job site, We will definitely respond back to everyone that contacts us as soon as possible ). 

Valentini Kitchens and the Pasquariello Family had its own hot reality TV series called "Building Family" in 2005 on HGTV Canada. This series aired weekly nationwide with a total of 6 half hour episodes. Please click here on the Homestars Valentini Kitchens Video Galleries to watch the episodes and to read up more on this, please visit our website. 
 
We hope all of our past and future customers enjoy watching this show as it shows the everyday life of our family business working together in the real world of Kitchen Manufacturing and Home Renovations with a flare of true reality in our day to day activities.

Modular Home Additions has developed a revolutionary concept using sophisticated computer software and building techniques. In just days, a second storey addition or new home, custom designed to your needs, can be built. All structural building parts are designed and built in a climate controlled environment. This enables us to have a high quality level and build all year round without leaving your house vulnerable to weather conditions. There is minimal noise, dust and no mess.
Combining technology with excellent service, achieving your dreams is easier, faster and affordable. Using factory built components can save you up to 30% compared to conventional methods. This one-stop approach to renovating is a wise choice amongst many alternatives and gives you the optimum value for your home.

profile:
Why choose The Renovators of Canada?  
 
For over the past 20 years our focus on customer experience has helped The Renovators of Canada grow to locations in Durham, Aurora, Stouffville, Markham, Vaughan, Toronto, Hamilton, Guelph, Kitchener, Waterloo, Barrie, Oshawa, Oakville and Cambridge. 
 
Unique to the industry, The Renovators of Canada provides a 10 year warranty on all craftsmanship. This home renovation warranty protection was established to provide peace of mind as home and business owners contemplate renovating a personal or commercial space. 
 
T-ROC is a fully licensed and insured including WSIB. Other affiliations include memberships with the National Kitchen and Bath Association, CARAHS, Better Business Bureau.  
 
We have a proven track record working with our customers with full transparency in every aspect of your project.  Can’t be present all the time during the renovation process?  No worries, we have specialized client software that allows you to see the entire schedule and pictures as the project happens in real time. We care for your home like it’s our own and always conduct ourselves respectfully and professionally.  
 
With our motivated and innovative professionals we will transform your house and make your dream home a reality.  Visit our website at www.trocanada.com

profile:
RM Renovation is a Toronto based renovation company with more than 20 years experience in the field.
.
WE ARE THE TEAM OF PROFESSIONALS WHO PERFORM KITCHEN, BATH OR BASEMENT RENOVATIONS ACCORDING TO YOUR PERSONAL PROJECT.
.
Our major activities are renovating basements, kitchens and bathrooms at reasonable prices. Trusting such works to us our clients have convinced in their quality and fast performing. We provide high-quality construction and renovation services as well as give maximum guarantee for our services. Depending on the project we perform our interior design, wall insulation and finishing.

Our advantages:

Quality and efficiency. We provide preparing and performing works as soon as possible.
Years of experience. We are in the renovation services market for many years and have an excellent reputation and hundreds of grateful customers.
Individual approach. We approach responsibly to perform each order and find the best options for the task as well as advise customers in order to meet all their individual needs.
Highly qualified specialists. We are a team of professionals and perform our work efficiently and reliably. Our employees keep their skills always according to the up to date requirements.
Customers positive reviews. We have a lot of positive feedback from the customers.
.
.
Basement renovation:

Basement in a private house more often perceived as a technical room: storeroom for garden tools or a cellar to store the harvest. Meanwhile, the basement is easy can turn into a full room to organize here, for example, a vinotheque, bar, home theatre or billiard room. The kitchen in the basement is also becoming a very popular modern solution. Construction and repair of the basement or ground floor, of course, will transform your home by adding not only the living space but also personality.

The following work can be done during the basement renovation.

Waterproofing. This is necessary if the moisture on the room walls revealed.

Heating. If the room is designed for staying long (kitchen, library, bathroom), it should be warm enough in any case.

Thermal insulation. This feature will save on heating and prevent heat loss into the ground and it will greatly enhance the energy efficiency of the whole building.

Lighting. If the basement has a small level above the soil it can be equipped with energy-saving windows. Additional electric light point sources using LED lamps will be created as well.

Soundproofing will be installed if the basement room contains equipment that generates big noise (e.g. water pumps etc.).

Water supply and sewerage. These works are performed accordingly to the local water company. Additional pumps can be installed if necessary.

Networks for the power supply, LAN or television can be laid, so it will provide you with maximum comfort.
.
.
Kitchen renovation:

The kitchen is one of the most visited places in your house. That is why it is so important that this room should be cozy and functional. We will do for you all kinds of our works for any areas of the rooms, from small to large ones. These will be the following:

1. Replacing the wires.

2. Aligning the surfaces of the ceiling and walls.

3. Laying the floor and wall tiles.

4. Floor, ceiling and general kitchen equipment installation.

5. Kitchen windows replacement.

6. Home appliances integration.

We always use safe and easy to wash materials.
.
.
Bathrooms renovation:

We are trying to renovate the bathroom as soon as possible because we well know this room is essentially the most important thing in your home. This type of repair involves the following:

1. Initial preparing the room, dismounting the wires, old tiles and plumbing communications.

2. Installation of new wiring, plumbing pipes, risers.

3. Preparing the walls, floor and ceiling.

4. Installation the new door and windows.

5. Installing the tiles on the floor and walls.

6. Installation of the new ceiling and lighting.

7. Installation of new connections to the water supply and sanitation.

8. Installation of all sanitary equipment and electric wash machine if needed.

We work at any time convenient for you. We are looking forward to meeting you!
specialities: Kitchen Renovation; Bathroom Renovation; Basement Renovation; Full House Renovations

profile:
Gala Renovations was founded with the concept born out of two sound principles: client-centred design and impeccable customer service. Whether your space is wide open with room to imagine, or small and cozy where we have to be creative, we will work with you to ensure that your renovation is completed exactly the way you want it. Our process starts with the ideas and vision you have for your home and moves to our team who will create plans that will guide our craftsmen to build the home of your dreams.


We specialize in complete home, ground and second floor renovations but we also take on other projects like basements, attics, custom kitchens, bathrooms, wall units, and storage solutions. We are flexible and collaborative in our approach and we care about the details that will ultimately beautify your home. At Gala, we leave no stone unturned in the journey from concept to reality. Our passion and knowledge paired with your dwelling and vision, will culminate in a one-of-a kind, unique space that you can proudly call home!

profile:
For all your flooring needs!

Headquartered in Toronto Ontario Canada; MST is one of the pre-eminent flooring companies operating in the southern Ontario region. Our main focus at MST is to cater to the customer and provide them with exactly what they need and want.

Day or night, local or out of town, we are the best choice for your flooring needs.

Founded in 2016, MST has grown to become a leader in flooring installation, family owned and operated since its start is what makes MST the great company it is, and your number one choice.

With regards to this unsteady market and with full awareness of our clients expenditures involved in this new market place MST rates are still one of the most competitive in the market.

Wether it is private, public, residential, commercial, large or small we will confidently take on any project and with almost 2 decades of experience, complete that project to your satisfaction…. We won't leave until you are completely satisfied – it is our guarantee!

When you entrust MST with your project we will utilize every inch of space in an innovative aesthetic and functional manner, giving you the exact look that you or your clients are aiming for.

Our reputation of having a solution-focused project team to deliver optimum service is another factor, which sets as apart from our competitors. Working on some of Toronto's greatest landmarks and with major corporations has given MST a firm grasp on client driven results under the most rigorous schedules and time frames.

How would you like new floors, enclosures, and backsplashes that reflect uniqueness and appeal throughout your residential or commercial property? Count on our company, MST, for detailed tiling work that breathes more life into your home or business. MST excels in tile installations that provide more wonder for your interior while also modernizing your property's decor.

profile:
For all your flooring needs!

Headquartered in Toronto Ontario Canada; MST is one of the pre-eminent flooring companies operating in the southern Ontario region. Our main focus at MST is to cater to the customer and provide them with exactly what they need and want.

Day or night, local or out of town, we are the best choice for your flooring needs.

Founded in 2016, MST has grown to become a leader in flooring installation, family owned and operated since its start is what makes MST the great company it is, and your number one choice.

With regards to this unsteady market and with full awareness of our clients expenditures involved in this new market place MST rates are still one of the most competitive in the market.

Wether it is private, public, residential, commercial, large or small we will confidently take on any project and with almost 2 decades of experience, complete that project to your satisfaction…. We won't leave until you are completely satisfied – it is our guarantee!

When you entrust MST with your project we will utilize every inch of space in an innovative aesthetic and functional manner, giving you the exact look that you or your clients are aiming for.

Our reputation of having a solution-focused project team to deliver optimum service is another factor, which sets as apart from our competitors. Working on some of Toronto's greatest landmarks and with major corporations has given MST a firm grasp on client driven results under the most rigorous schedules and time frames.

How would you like new floors, enclosures, and backsplashes that reflect uniqueness and appeal throughout your residential or commercial property? Count on our company, MST, for detailed tiling work that breathes more life into your home or business. MST excels in tile installations that provide more wonder for your interior while also modernizing your property's decor.

profile:
Excellent Quality at a Fair Price
Properly installed fencing creates safety for your children, safety for your pets.  Properly installed decking creates beautiful and functional outdoor living space for you to enjoy with family and friends.  Why work with Ajax Fence Ltd?

We offer quality work at a fair price.

A fence is an investment in your home’s value, so you want it to stand the test of time. We can provide references from customers we've worked with over the past 40 years. We build to last. Our workmanship is excellent, so you’re never left chasing after a company for repairs.  We never overinflate our prices – we have been building fences right for over 40 years, at a fair price.

We hire only experienced full time staff.

At Ajax Fence our staff are fully experienced... some have been building fences right for close to 40 years! Employing only experienced fence builders ensures every fence is built to our exacting standards – and will last.

We only use quality materials, and do not skimp.

While some companies may offer lower prices, our jobs are priced fairly while providing proper construction using quality materials. A fence board can be installed using only one nail, or it can be done correctly to ensure it lasts.

We have history and connection.

Mark Pierson started Ajax Fence and oversees every quote, every job site and is often hands on.  We're excited that the next generation, Derek Pierson, is now taking an active role in the operation of the company.  You know who you’re working with, who is in charge of the job, and you know it will be installed correctly.

As there is no governing body for fence building – be clear of the details on any quotes you receive.  Is the installer experienced?  Does the company qualify for a current WSIB clearance certificate?  Does the company carry adequate commercial liability insurance?  Are future repair costs going to outweigh your initial savings on a lower quality of workmanship and product?

Call or email now for QUALITY fence and deck installation.

Owning a home is one of the most important financial and sentimental assets that one can have. Beyond building a financially reliable base, you want a home to match your lifestyle and your dreams. When you work with TK Contracting, you’re going to be getting a service that exceeds all expectations through our licensed and bonded tradespeople. 

Our Company
We at TK Contracting Inc.  Are passionate about the work we do. Our commitment is to work with our clients in order to achieve the best results in the project with a safe and timely manner.  We are dedicated to provide our clients with a high level of satisfaction. 

Heath and Safety Protocols
Our policy at TK Contracting is to maintain a safe working environment for everyone. Compliance with health and safety regulations are all outlined in the health and safety policy of TK Contracting.  Our employees are all trained yearly to follow these safety protocols. In order to reduce the risk of injuries at the workplace. 

COVID19 Precautions 
To keep our clients and workers safe, all workers will have a temperature check, and a log to record. All workers shall sanitize before Jobsite, and wear a mask during the entire day. TK Contracting makes sure every team member is tested before working. We are one of the few companies who follow these precautions.

Guaranteed Workmanship 
Our company ensures that each project is handled with good quality materials and professional knowledge to achieve the highest level of satisfaction. We provide a quality service on every project. TK Contracting offers a free written guarantee of 12 months from the date of completion.

The Preferred Home and Bath (PHAB) family works to improve the quality of life of our customers in the form of well-designed, well-planned, and well-executed interior renovations. We strive to create trusted, ongoing relationships with our customers that see them through every life stage of home ownership from their 1st home reno to their forever home.

PLANNING AND PERMITTING
Preferred Home and Bath has decades of experience with the Ontario Building Code and will always follow its principles by default.

DESIGN
Our designer will first create your space, to scale, in 3D so that you can collaborate on the best possible layout for your lifestyle. Guided material selections will help you create a warm and inviting atmosphere that matches your personal style.

PROJECT MANAGEMENT
Our project managers have years of hands-on construction knowledge that pair perfectly with modern project management techniques to create a seamless process that always produces a happy customer. We value our continued relationship.

profile:
Experience generations of expertise, flawless workmanship, and customer service excellence. For over thirty years, we have used our eco-friendly synthetic turf products to enhance our clients’ spaces.

As one of the key pioneers in the synthetic turf industry in Canada, our passion is providing our clients with spaces where they can relax, enjoy and play – safely and worry free!

We are experts in golf turf, and have worked with some of the most prestigious golf courses in Toronto, GTA and York Region. Our understanding of golf playability is unmatched, and we have worked with golf clubs like Diamond Back in preparation of multiple sites hosting the Canadian PGA Championships.

As irrigation specialists, we understand how to properly deal with water and drainage so you don’t have to. When working with any outdoor element, drainage is one of the most important things to consider and do correctly to get the results you want.

Above all else, we are dedicated to delivering the highest quality products combined with our superior installations and outstanding customer service.

profile:
Dorval Homes is a high-end custom building company specializing in new homes, additions, and renovations in the Greater Toronto Area.  With over 10 years in the GTA, our rich heritage isn’t to be understated – and discerning homeowners and leading architects have come to rely on Dorval Homes for exquisite attention to detail and comprehensive knowledge of master home-building.  

The happiness of our customers is our singular goal.  Creating joy in our customers’ experience is the byproduct of combining our superior building systems with a rugged moral code emphasizing honesty and fairness.  

Dorval Homes is highly conscious of a project timeline and budget and has proven methods for delivering on both.  These advantages are conveyed to each client through a dedicated team and a highly transparent project management process.  

Additionally, Dorval Homes' 3-year warranty reflects our higher level of service after the job is done, as well as confidence in our craftsmanship.  This means that if there is any follow-up work, or request, long after a project has been completed, we promptly take care of it.  Think of us as your long-term, accountable partner.

profile:
At Mignon Interiors, we Design, get your Permits and Approvals, and Build your Home.
Do you need a Full Home Renovation, New Construction, Extension, Addition, Second Floor, Basement or Kitchen Renovation?

We begin with a Free Consultation in your Home. We want to learn about your current layout, design and structural features. We also want to know what you do and don't like about your home. Next our Designer will do an extensive brainstorming of possible designs, colour tones and layouts. She will put together a proposal and recommend what styles go well with your home and preferences. The planning and design is the most important part of a home renovation. 

Next we have a Contractor with over 40 years of construction experience in Toronto. He will look at all the structural changes, interior and exterior finishes etc. to calculate your construction cost. We work with you and make adjustments until you are satisfied with the scope of your renovation and budget. Everything is on paper, we do not touch your home until you give us your approval. 

We then put together a rigid timeline and schedule. Materials are sourced and contractors begin their work. To keep your money safe, we want to minimize up front deposits and pay progress payments only after each stage is completed. Our goal is to keep you informed throughout the entire process, whilst allowing you to focus on your daily work, family and social life.

Welcome to Mignon Interiors, where we stand by our reputation. We are dedicated to giving you a positive experience and make sure you will be thrilled with your Brand New Home.

profile:
At Mignon Interiors, we Design, get your Permits and Approvals, and Build your Home.
Do you need a Full Home Renovation, New Construction, Extension, Addition, Second Floor, Basement or Kitchen Renovation?

We begin with a Free Consultation in your Home. We want to learn about your current layout, design and structural features. We also want to know what you do and don't like about your home. Next our Designer will do an extensive brainstorming of possible designs, colour tones and layouts. She will put together a proposal and recommend what styles go well with your home and preferences. The planning and design is the most important part of a home renovation. 

Next we have a Contractor with over 40 years of construction experience in Toronto. He will look at all the structural changes, interior and exterior finishes etc. to calculate your construction cost. We work with you and make adjustments until you are satisfied with the scope of your renovation and budget. Everything is on paper, we do not touch your home until you give us your approval. 

We then put together a rigid timeline and schedule. Materials are sourced and contractors begin their work. To keep your money safe, we want to minimize up front deposits and pay progress payments only after each stage is completed. Our goal is to keep you informed throughout the entire process, whilst allowing you to focus on your daily work, family and social life.

Welcome to Mignon Interiors, where we stand by our reputation. We are dedicated to giving you a positive experience and make sure you will be thrilled with your Brand New Home.

profile:
Hello Viewer! 

We offer full turn key solutions for interiors and exterior renovations for a variety of building types. Working at a range of scales, from custom renovation projects for residential market to adaptive reuse of small commercial buildings. The team lists beauty, practicality, and social and environmental sustainability as essentials for ‘healthier and happier buildings’.  


We specialize in the design and renovation management of a variety of spaces which can differ in size and function.  It is through our free consultation that  a picture is painted on what your project and budgetary requirements are.   We will hold your hand as tight as you require and ensure that we listen to your wants and needs.  Once we have a clear picture of scope and budget, our team will estimate and design your space for you accordingly with years of experience and education backing our every decision.   


There is no project to small and no renovation project to large for us to handle.  
-We work with a variety of agents who have clients moving into their new 2 story properties or condos which have very tight time lines.  We have accomplished full 3 story (including basement) renovations in 5 weeks flats when necessary.  
-We have many recurring clients which use our services for each challenge they face.  If you aren't ready to do a full project in a single swing,  we can help you break down the project into proper stepping stones to spend where necessary and when necessary. 


We are a phone call or email away and would be honored to work with you.

Welcome to ZAFCON INC your professional expert contractor. 

WHO WE ARE
Our company team consist of project managers, engineers, designers, construction and renovation specialists who are experts in their field. This team has worked successfully together to help our customers achieve their construction objective and dream renovations.

OUR CORE VALUES

Safety - We are commitment to safety to ensure everyone can return to their loved ones at the end of the day. As a result, we ensure all team members and all work is in compliance with safety regulations,  WSIB and Covid-19 protocols.

Quality - Quality distinguishes best from the rest. Our craftsmanship approach ensures that all of our clients receive nothing but the best quality service.

Integrity - We don't take the convenient approach but rather the RIGHT one, even if no one is watching.  

Transparency - The most important core value for us is to ensure our customers receive clear terms and conditions upfront. This will help us build long lasting relationships which further fosters our team culture across all levels of skills and management. 

Services we offer:

Full Home Renovations

profile:
Welcome to Open Concept 

The company specializes in structural engineering and renovations. OCEC LTD was founded to be able to help others live their lives without unwanted obstructions. It may be a wall, a duct hump or post in the basement that is in the way of your pool table or a home gym or simply in the middle of a room. Whatever the case may be it’s not IM'possible. Our innovative approach to basement post removal has been designed and approved by qualified engineers with many satisfied customers. The method does not require any welding or major beam replacements. We have also made it possible through our ingenuity to be able to sink beams into the joists to have a perfectly flat ceiling finish on both the first and/or second floors of your home.

We are an insured business from both and engineering and construction stand point. 

Liability Insurance on Construction and Engineering Services. 

We're social here:

https://www.facebook.com/ocecltd
https://twitter.com/OpenConceptEng1

profile:
About Us
Hausvio Inc is a leading Toronto-based home renovations company. We pride ourselves on our eco-friendly, innovative, and professional approach to all of our home renovation projects. From a brand new kitchen or bathroom to whole house projects, our team works hard to transform your living spaces completely.
​
We believe in a more personal approach to home renovation projects. By working closely with our clients, understanding their goals, and working hard to craft solution-focused designs allows us to create beautifully crafted, functional living spaces.
OUR TEAM
The Hausvio is made of professional, experienced carpenters with over a decade in the industry. Each member is well-known and admired in their field for exceptional quality, attention to detail, and talent. We also collaborate with other local professionals, including Architects, Engineers, Kitchen & Bathroom Designers, Electricians, Plumbers, and other specialized personnel, to guarantee we are providing the highest level of service and care for our clients.

MEET THE FOUNDER
Owner/ CEO Wilson is a Licenced Professional Engineer with over five years of experience in the home renovation field. Wilson is passionate about implementing the best methods and practices to help reduce Hausvio’s carbon footprint.

Hausvio is pursuing a LEED (Leadership in Energy and Environmental Design) Certificate. LEED is the most widely used green building rating system in Canada and across the globe. LEED is a proven and holistic path to addressing climate change. At Hausvio, we’re committed to creating more resource-efficient, healthy, and resilient homes without compromising design aesthetics, quality, or living convenience.

WHY GO GREEN
Protects Our Ecosystem: Efficient Use of Resources & Energy
Healthier Indoor Environment: Improved Quality of Life
Energy-Efficient: Reduced Operational Cost and Maintenance
Lower Maintenance and Operation Costs
Reduces Strain on Local Resources
services:
Our Services
Your home should perfectly reflect your style, taste, and lifestyle. We listen to your needs, goals, and visions and flawlessly align them with the best building practices to deliver the best possible outcomes for your living spaces.
Kitchen
The kitchen is the heartbeat of the home. At Hausvio, we create kitchens that work for your family, design choices, and your way of living. From contemporary and modern renovations to open concepts and traditional styles, Hausvio works with you to create beautiful, functional kitchens that complement your home’s aesthetic. 
 
Bathroom
Create a luxurious sanctuary in your home. Bathrooms are a place where you can relax, refresh, and rejuvenate. Our team has experience remodeling various bathroom styles, including ensuites, power rooms, and main bathrooms. Whether you want to create a spa-like oasis with a thermostatic shower system or just refresh your cabinetry, our team can help. 
Whole House
Let us help you make your house a home. If you need significant upgrades to your living space to make it work for you and your family, we offer complete house renovations. Typically, whole house renovations include major elements like the kitchen, bathrooms, interior finishes, flooring, and mechanical systems (electrical, plumbing, and HVAC). 
Basement
Finished basements add additional living space while significantly increasing your property value. We offer fully customizable basement renovations to fit your needs. Our team can add vital functional living space and much-needed storage to upgrade your lifestyle. To add even more value to your home, talk to us about including sub-flooring, lighting, a wet bar, laundry room, built-ins, and upgrading insulation.

profile:
"My Prestigious Home" is where you need to be...

MPH has been a leader in major renovations and custom home construction since 2007. From concept to completion, we take a client’s vision and make it a reality through a comprehensive process to ensure the finished product exceeds expectations. Choosing a reputable contractor is the most important decision you will make regarding your project and better to say, your investment. From plans and permits, to last little finishing details, MPH is committed to completing your renovations and home improvements in a professional manner and to your complete satisfaction.

Our vast professional experience, skilled expertise and attention to details enable us to offer you innovative solutions, competitive pricing and the ability to meet milestones. We appreciate how much your project means to you. That’s why we approach each project with professionalism, integrity and adaptability while maintaining open communication with you every step of the way.
We pride ourselves in Home additions, renovations, custom home building, commercial renovations, condominium renovations and design and build projects.

We understand custom homes and renovations are amongst the most important investment to people in their lifetime. So whether it be a new architecturally designed or inspired home, or a renovation and extension of your existing home, you can be guaranteed that MPH is most definitely the qualified team for your project.

We have had the opportunity to transform your dreams into reality by designing rooms where you can relax and your children can safely play. We have enjoyed being a part of homeowners’ lives and strive to continue to provide our customers with the best technology on the market. We have completed literally hundreds of renovations since our inception. 

Please view our website at http://MyPrestigiousHome.com to view images of some of our projects.

Regardless of scope, we approach every single home renovation with a foundation of strong design aesthetics, comprehensive product options, sound project management, and a commitment to craftsmanship.

Our projects range from building new custom homes, home additions and extensions, condominium renovations, architectural design and permit, structural engineering, commercial renovations, rear addition, second floor addition, basement underpinning, custom kitchen and bathrooms, residential renovations and finally we design and build everything. We take pride in our personalized service and our high quality workmanship.

With 2 year Warranty, we at MPH know how to design and build lasting results and lasting relationships with each of our highly respected clients.

Our focus is on Custom projects such as custom Kitchen renovations, Basement Finishing and underpinning, Bathroom Renovation and Bathroom Remodeling, Home Additions, Second Story Additions, Rear Additions, Home Extensions and Rear Extensions, commercial renovations, office renovation, architectural drawings, permit and etc. We work with some of the top architects, interior designers, engineers and sub-trades in Toronto. We are the all inclusive General Contractor who will take care of all your design and general contracting needs.

MPH is an innovative, full service design/build/construction firm based in Toronto, specializing in residential clients across the GTA. With decades of construction management experience on a wide variety of residential projects, we offer a strong design aesthetic, invaluable insight, vast resources and craftsman that exceed client expectations.

Strong leadership and communication skills are the essential components necessary to navigate a construction project from concept to completion. Our extensive knowledge of all trade areas involved in both new construction and sophisticated renovations have proven invaluable to our company and our clients. Our recognition of the importance of scheduling, cost control, and quality control underlies and defines our successful completion of many challenging projects on time and within budget.

There are many different reasons to work with us: to make room for a growing family, to improve layout or increase the resale value of your property! Our team of professionals offer customers design and build counselling along with skilled trades and top discounts, on top brands.

There is no substitute for experience. Join the list of satisfied clients! In the end the quality of your project depends on who you hire. When you hire us, you do so because of our company’s reputation, our track record with past clients and our commitment to new ones.

Contact us for a free "No Pressure" estimate and let us help you take the first step to completing your project. Advice is always free. Remember, we are talking about Professional Advice from Skilled Engineer.
Our areas of servings are in Toronto, Beaches, Etobicoke, Mississauga, Richmond hill, Markham, Foresthill, Royal York, Vaughan, Woodbridge, East York, West end, Central Toronto, North York, & Downtown Toronto.

profile:
OUR PROCESS

 

When working with GTCC, you will have access to knowledgeable professionals working cohesively to provide you with a finished product you can be proud of for years to come. We will provide honest answers and insights to any questions or querries you have throughout the process.

First, you will start with a free consultation and estimate. This is where we will go over all of your options and approximate budgets. If you're seeking help with a smaller renovation (kitchen, bathroom, basement), we will provide you a fixed price in this phase.

Should you decide to move forward with us for a custom home addition design paclage, you will then move into the design phase. This is where you will meet with our architects and designers and together come up with a uniquely custom-tailored plan for your new custom renovation or addition.

Once we have engineered drawings for your project, we will then cost the project based on these approved drawings and provide you with a fixed price to execute the work in a timely fashion.

When we have agreed on the scope of work and price the real planning for us begins. We will provide you a project schedule and approximate start and completion date. Product will be ordered and we will be on our way.

Throughout the construction phase of the project, we will be in constant contact with you. We will keep you apprised of any pertinent information regarding your project through email and set weekly meetings.

When the work is complete, we will do a final walkthrough to discuss any potential deficiencies that must be fixed (on our dollar) and hand over the keys to your new home.

Customer Satisfaction Guaranteed

From the moment you phone us through the completion of your landscaping project, our professionals will make sure that your experience with us is top-notch. Our team pays special attention to all details in projects and will regularly communicate with you till the project is complete. Our priority is to ensure the complete satisfaction of every client.  

We are trained to help clients increase the value and curb appeal of their homes by creating an outdoor environment beyond their imagination. We work together to create elegant landscape designs with the help of our team of landscape designers. We work closely with our customers when designing the space to ensure the complete satisfaction of the results of their project.   

Get In touch!

We strive to be in constant communication with our customers until the job is done. If you have questions or special requests, just drop us a line. profile:
At onlyRENOS we understand that deciding to renovate your home is one of the biggest decisions your family will ever make! It’s important to find a company you can trust to bring your vision to life, while keeping the process under professional supervision from start to finish. 

Our initial consultation with you and your family will be an in-depth analysis of the vision and ideas you have for your renovation. We will also be able to provide you with the preliminary scope of work for your project, including a rough estimate along with outlining the necessary building permit applications that would be needed in order to begin working on your renovation project.

During this consultation, our architects, engineers and project managers, will all assess your project in order to lay-out every aspect of your renovation. This consultation includes, but is not limited to, a detailed scope of work, preliminary architectural drawings, engineer report, budgeting and payment schedule. Oftentimes our clients are also interested in our interior design services relating to the finishing materials, colours, kitchen and bathroom fixtures, lighting fixtures, furniture and home decor.

profile:
LUMAT is a family operated construction company with 20 years of experience building dream homes that customers admire, and are proud to call thiers . Every home we build is uniquely sculped to our clients needs, wants and budget, although, every project we take on is consistent in the care and quality conveyed from start to finish. We are a small Father and Son company who have built dream homes for clients all over Toronto, only from word of mouth from client to client, who have raved about our worksmanship. We make it a point to only build a few homes at a time, this is to ensure the highest attention to detail for our clients at all times, setting us aside from most contractors. We at LUMAT are experts in the intricate process of building homes from start to finish and our goal is to eliminate the stress from homeowners by keeping you fully informed and as comfortable as possible throughout every phase of the construction process. This has worked great for us and our clients over the years, and its allowed us to not only build some of the most breathtaking luxury custom homes in the GTA but also extend valuable peace of mind to each of our charished clients. LUMAT Construction Ltd. provides custom home building services and full-scale renovations. From conception to possession, LUMAT's dedicated team of licenced tradesmen can guide and assist you through the entire project and provide cost-savings through our long-time relationships with all our trade partners we consistently contract and trust. Come check out one of our builds, and see what LUMAT is really all about!
 
 
 

My family sincerely looks forward to working with you, and cant wait to help you turn your dream home into a reality.
 
 
 

"Your Home, Our Passion"

profile:
At First Canadian Construction Corp, we specialize in creating complete customized home renovation solutions. Whether it’s your investment project or it’s your family home, after a free initial consultation and space analysis, our designers will present you with a set of options customized to fit your needs and budget. 
We cover everything from design to installation, and every single phase of the project is supervised to ensure it stays on schedule and meets our standard of excellence.
If you’re looking for a complete home remodel or just partial renovation, count on us for professional services. 

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Remodeling for Home Owners
You are updating your house into something new to meet your family's requirements or changing the layout and use of a space to increase your overall space function, or you are just restoring your home to good condition and making the look new again with some cosmetic upgrades, we help you achieve your goal within your planned budget.
We start with a meeting to hear about your requirements and your goals. Then we show you our previous works and our process, detailing all the steps we are going to take to make this project easy and enjoyable for you and your family.
After conducting a house survey, we will provide you with some designs options and associate budget.
During the process, we are with you all through the project to make sure you are kept up to date on all activities and that you and your family's concerns are in the forefront.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Remodeling for Investors:

If you are an investor who carefully choose and owns your own investment properties and you are planning to remodel or renovate to increase the value and earn the profit, we will be focused on those details that will result in the most value for the least amount of effort and cost.
Part of the process includes a market and neighborhood analysis, paying close attention to the other homes in the neighborhood to avoid over-improving the property or spending budget and effort on the spaces that doesn’t boost the value.

******

Our team of real estate professionals will survey the neighborhood and its potential to architect your remodeling approach and define a plan to maximize the investment profit.
This remolding plan is focused on increasing profit for our investors and not ours. We take benefit from our long lasting relationships.

******
Once our market analysis for your property is complete, you will be provided with our recommendations, the layout changes and any required upgrades including choosing right finishes for each room. All the details will be fully documented for your review and approval.

profile:
BRIKS (Verb/ Noun/ Adjective): Bespoke. The Art of Luxury, Redefined.

BRIKS Design-Build Group is a TARION Registered Boutique Firm, specializing in Luxury New Build Construction of Custom Residences. We offer a Full range of the Best-in-Class General Contracting Services, including Transitional Renovation and Remodeling, Kitchen Designs, and Interior Design for Residential and Commercial Clients throughout Toronto.

The construction of your home may well be the largest investment you ever make, and is a huge undertaking. Simply put, this is not the type of job in which you can leave anything to chance. When you work with BRIKS Design & Build for your new and remodeling construction projects in the G.T.A., nothing will be overlooked. 
With our experienced team of renowned Architects, Interior Designers, Engineers, and Sub- Trades; we assure you that every detail of the construction project, from initial designs to site plans, and from construction to the materials sourced and used; will only be of the highest level of caliber that we work with. Whatever your vision of your new home may entail, our bespoke BRIKS team will ensure that it is fully realized.
As a leading Design-Build Firm in the G.T.A. , not only do we provide detailed site and architectural plans from some of the most reputable Architects in Canada, but we also assist with every part of the building process. From applying for permits, to laying the foundation, to your BRIKS Pre-Delivery Inspection; we are truly your one-stop shop for all your construction needs. 
Over the last 20+ years, we’ve earned the trust of residents throughout the G.T.A. region, and we would love an opportunity to earn your trust and business.

My Mission is to help bring your dreams/visions to life while working within your budget. I believe anything is possible.  Our team/crew is constantly researching new building trends and design techniques so we can share them with you. I built this company based on affordable pricing and extreme attention to detail.  I love educating  clients as questions come up, regarding our process during your installation.  I understand, through my 10 years of experience, that changes come up and I work with you on  getting your finished product exactly how you want it.  I offer free estimates and typically meet a few additional times before, depending on the project size.  My crew and I are very meticulous when it comes to detail, spacing, cutting, and finishing. profile:
Falcon Contracting, a privately owned company founded in 1987 by John Giannopoulos, is among the leading general contracting companies serving the Greater Toronto Metropolitan region. As a "hands on" builder, Falcon Contracting has the experience, expertise, and, above all, the passion to deliver quality building solutions for a wide array of constrcution projects.

Owner and founder John Giannopolous, has an extensive background in the construction industry dating back to the early 1980s. Prior to establishing Falcon Contracting, John specialized for five years in window, door and storefront installations in high-rise, commerical and residential projects.

Since its inception as a one-man operation in 1987, Falcon Contracting has built a solid reputation for excellence and integrity in residential / commercial construction. This success can be attributed to John's dedication and passion for delivering superior performance value to clients based on exacting standards of quality, cost effectiveness and safety.

John's preconstruction know-how and techincal expertise in complex projects involving structural work, additions, 2nd story and custom homes enable him to anticipate project challenges and develop innovative solutions that ultimately fulfill and even surpass clients' objectives.

From concept to completion, Falcon Contracting has one single unwavering goal - customer satisfaction, 100% of the time.

Our services includes:

*Preconstruction Services: Design co-ordination, quality assurance, schedule control, cost analysis / budgeting, building systems analysis, site analysis /evaluation, client consultation, concept sketches, preliminary zoning investigation, production working drawings, obtain permits, zonign minor variance hearing preparation

*Project Planning: Developing preliminary critical path (project scheduling), design development / review, developing budget, trade procurement

*Construction Services: Design review & revision, building inspections, subcontractor coordination, budgeting and cost control, permitting and municipal approvals re: revision, contract administration, QA/ QC management, on site supervision

*Design/Build: Developing concept and design, producing working drawings, procurement management, subcontractor coordination, QA/QC management, cost monitoring and forecasting, safety inspections

*General Contracting: Contract administration, subcontractor prequalification & coordination, safety inspections, site management

*Renovation: Demolition and Disposal (Interior / Exterior), Excavations, Interiors, Rough and Finish carpentry, Masonry / Concrete work, Custom carpentry, Additions, second stories, custom homes, Landscaping, Kitchen & Bathroom Renovations, Basement Renovations

We clean and restore properties damaged from flood, fire, smoke, mold. Our team is certified and licensed in the emergency restoration field.

We also have lots of experience in the restoration field in houses and businesses all around GTA and northern Ontario.

Our responsibility is to inform and communicate with you about all cleaning and restoration procedures we follow. Also we are here to answer any other questions you might have for us. We offer restoration services 24/7 according to your needs.

profile:
ABOUT SHANDYMAN CONTRACTING

ShandyMan Contracting is one of Toronto's most trusted General Contractors, specializing in Roofing, Painting and Carpentry & Renovations.

Whether it be a commercial or residential design or repair, The ShandyMan Team prides themselves on their results and happy customers.

CORE VALUES

PEOPLE
This core value runs deep in the Shand family - passed down from Shane’s father who worked very hard to leave a legacy worth following. You can see it on the faces of friends, family, employees and customers of ShandyMan Contracting Inc. Love and leadership is at the centre of this organization.

PASSION
One has to be passionate about their craft in order to be successful in this business - it can be tough and the work isn’t always pretty. For anyone who’s ever worked with "The ShandyMan", the first thing you’ll notice is his passion for life, family and work. Passion is wildly reflected in ShandyMan Contracting’s long lasting relationships and successful projects across the Greater Toronto Area.

PURPOSE
Founder, Shane Shand truly believes in living a life of purpose and meaning. ShandyMan Contracting provides that opportunity for its employees through the example Shane and his team have been setting from an early age. Growing up in Toronto’s Beaches, and learning from his father, he now brings over 20 years of experience as a General Contractor with key specialities. Shane is now able to live out his own dream through the art of enhancing commercial and residential properties.

SHANE SHAND
FOUNDER & PRESIDENT

THE SHANDYMAN STORY
MEET OUR FOUNDER & PRESIDENT SHANE SHAND THE "SHANDYMAN"
Born and raised in Toronto's Beaches Community, Shane and his team bring over 20 years of experience in residential and commercial General Contracting. ShandyMan Contracting services a variety of clients across the Greater Toronto Area and beyond. Specialties include; roofing, painting and carpentry. ShandyMan's mission, vision and core values are the guide to transforming your space.

EVERY DAY IS A BLESSED DAY.

profile:
R&M Construction, founded in 1976 (incorporated in 1983), is a family owned and operated general contracting company based out of Acton, Ontario. We specialize in the construction and restoration of natural waterways including eroded banks and shorelines. Our goal is to restore the environment to the way it was originally created, protect infrastructure, and improve habitat in an efficient and cost effective manner while minimizing negative effects.

​

Projects include channel improvements, Storm Water Management (SWM) pond retro-fitting and creation, as well as protection of streams, wetlands, and shorelines, and the construction of soil erosion protection zones through bank stabilization. Our projects implement the latest in bio-engineering and fluvial geomorphologic designs to ensure they are completed to the highest standard and are ecologically stable. In addition to waterway restoration, we have also had the opportunity to rehabilitate and create parklands through the construction of trails, boardwalks, and pedestrian bridges.

​

Our team has extensive experience and expertise in the field, and are able to complete projects in highly sensitive and difficult to access areas.  We own a fleet of specialized equipment which has been outfitted specifically for this type of work as we continue to develop new and innovative methods. We have a team of construction professionals with years of experience in naturalized planting, waterway restoration, and impact minimization.

​

We have collaborated on projects with conservation authorities, municipalities, ministries, and private owners to ensure that shoreline protection and stream repairs are done professionally and quickly with as little environmental impact as possible.

​

Safety is a priority to us - we are continually reviewing our processes and policies while implementing new methods to ensure we are operating as safe as possible. We are COR Certified and have an active account with ISNetworld & Avetta. We are fully insured and bonded.

profile:
R&M Construction, founded in 1976 (incorporated in 1983), is a family owned and operated general contracting company based out of Acton, Ontario. We specialize in the construction and restoration of natural waterways including eroded banks and shorelines. Our goal is to restore the environment to the way it was originally created, protect infrastructure, and improve habitat in an efficient and cost effective manner while minimizing negative effects.

​

Projects include channel improvements, Storm Water Management (SWM) pond retro-fitting and creation, as well as protection of streams, wetlands, and shorelines, and the construction of soil erosion protection zones through bank stabilization. Our projects implement the latest in bio-engineering and fluvial geomorphologic designs to ensure they are completed to the highest standard and are ecologically stable. In addition to waterway restoration, we have also had the opportunity to rehabilitate and create parklands through the construction of trails, boardwalks, and pedestrian bridges.

​

Our team has extensive experience and expertise in the field, and are able to complete projects in highly sensitive and difficult to access areas.  We own a fleet of specialized equipment which has been outfitted specifically for this type of work as we continue to develop new and innovative methods. We have a team of construction professionals with years of experience in naturalized planting, waterway restoration, and impact minimization.

​

We have collaborated on projects with conservation authorities, municipalities, ministries, and private owners to ensure that shoreline protection and stream repairs are done professionally and quickly with as little environmental impact as possible.

​

Safety is a priority to us - we are continually reviewing our processes and policies while implementing new methods to ensure we are operating as safe as possible. We are COR Certified and have an active account with ISNetworld & Avetta. We are fully insured and bonded.

profile:
Kitchen Nation

Kitchen Nation is a design and build company which services in the Greater Toronto Area and the surrounding cities. For over 2 decades, our dynamic team of award-winning professionals has been guiding the clients through the process of renovating a property of their dreams. 
Our team prides itself on creating elegant, timeless, and welcoming spaces that complement the lifestyle and budget of the clients. Our design aesthetic is effortless, we combine creativity and functionality.
Being the best at the craft is what we strike for. From custom renovations to commercial projects, our team is here for you at every step of the way. 


WHAT DO WE OFFER?

1.	Exquisite/Variety of designs
2.	21+ years of expertise
3.	High-end finishes
4.	Incomparable quality
5.	Canadian manufacturing 
6.	In-house financing 
7.	Best price guarantee







OUR VALUES & APPROACH

CUSTOMER-DRIVEN APPROACH

Our experts focus on combining perfectionism with functionality. They complete each project with a team-playing and service-driven attitude. Our unique selling point is the ability to deliver smart and practical designs. While doing so, we keep your needs and wants in consideration. We pride ourselves in providing 100% customer satisfaction.

COMMITTED TEAM
One of our values is to provide clients with exceptional customer experience. To do so, we showcase full commitment to our work. From your first interaction with us to the last finishes, we believe in value service. 

DESIGN-BUILD MODEL

We draw every single one of our projects. We also focus on detailed design-driven models that allow us to provide you with a highly accurate estimate. We do not believe in guesswork and the accuracy is what makes us the trusted choice of our clients.  

QUALITY WORKMANSHIP
What might be considered an upgrade with other renovation companies is a standard with Interior Nation. We want you to end up with an elegant home that will stand the test of time. We believe in making a statement with our quality and craftsmanship. 

FEASIBILITY OF IN-HOUSE FINANCE
The ability for you to create a home that speaks to you, should be 100% attainable, however, we understand that interior renovations can be a financially stressful process. At Interior Nation, we are committed to helping you begin building the home of your dreams.


Know more, visit www.kitchennation.ca

- Client-focused: We ensure to do our best to meet our client’s satisfaction. We value the relationship between our clients. We are accountable, respectful, and effective for jobs assigned. We build trust with our clients through honesty, communication, and keeping our commitments.

- Flexibility: We are able to adapt to any working conditions and manage changes accordingly. We seek to provide the best solutions for our clients. We are open-minded to new innovations and ideas. We are optimistic, calm, and always plan ahead of what is to come.


Why Us?

- We are the ones on the site from start to finish, from the design phase to the project closeout. No surprises! No miscommunication between parties.
- We take care of all permits required, work closely with clients, and have trusted engineers that we have been working with for years.
- We have professionals in almost every trade including plumbing & electrical. No subcontractor markups!
- We will always provide professional advice to make sure any of your ideas won’t be troublesome later on!
- We have been in business for 16 years. Been built on referrals & returned clients!
